5000|$|Dellacroce {{was born}} in New York to Francesco and Antoinette Dellacroce, first {{generation}} immigrants from Italy. [...] He {{grew up in the}} Little Italy section of Manhattan. Dellacroce was a tall, broad-shouldered man who was usually chomping on a cigar. His nickname was [...] "Neil", an Americanization of [...] "Aniello". Due to his square-shaped face, some Gambino members nicknamed him [...] "the Polack", a nickname never used <b>within</b> his <b>earshot.</b>|$|R
